title: Loop1
---
//Variables setup
<<declare $loop = 1>>
<<declare $files = 0>>
//Start loop one; player is sitting at the computer with controls disabled; initial dialogue
<<disable_controls "Player">>
<<set_enabled_in_unity "PCCam" true>>
You: ...always the same view...day in, day out...
You: ...
You: You need this job-

<<set_enabled_in_unity "PhoneRing" true>> // plays sound of the phone
You: Ugh...
You: I was hoping he wouldn't bother me today. // this line exists so players actually listen to the phone ring
<<set_enabled_in_unity "PCCam" false>>
<<set_enabled_in_unity "PhoneCam" true>>
<<set_enabled_in_unity "PhonePickUp" true>> // plays sound of picking up the phone
You: ... // this line is here so that the pickup phone doesnt play AS he is saying "Hello"
You: Hello-

<<set_enabled_in_unity "Boss1part1" true>>
Boss: Took you long enough to respond! 
<<wait  0.5>>
<<set_enabled_in_unity "Boss1part2" true>>
Boss: You know I don't like incompetent employees, right?
<<wait  0.5>>

You: Yes, si-
<<set_enabled_in_unity "Boss2" true>>
Boss: That's what I thought. I need you to fetch me file 6G and 9E.
<<wait  3>>

<<set_enabled_in_unity "PhoneHangUp" false>>
<<set_enabled_in_unity "PhoneHangUp" true>> //plays the sound of hanging up the phone
<<set_enabled_in_unity "NoteLoop1" true>> //enable notepad UI for loop 1
You: *sigh*
<<set_enabled_in_unity "OfficeChair2" true>> //sound of the chair out
<<wait  0.5>>
<<set_enabled_in_unity "PhoneCam" false>>
You: Better get to work. 

<<enable_controls "Player">>
<<set_enabled_in_unity "TimerCanvas" true>>
//logically, move to ArchiveShelf11 node next
===

title: Loop2
---
//loop 2 dialogue - you should know the drill by now
<<disable_controls "Player">>
<<set_enabled_in_unity "PhoneCam" true>>
<<set_enabled_in_unity "OfficeChair1" false>> //sound of the chair out
<<set_enabled_in_unity "OfficeChair1" true>> //sound of the chair out
<<wait  2>>
